window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Chandler Brothers from </b><b><i>New York Times</i></b><b> best-selling author Carly Phillips are back!</b></p> <p><b><i>The Bachelor</i></b></p> <p>He’s got wanderlust and no intention of settling down.</p> <p>She’s home to stay and has put her bad-boy ex in her rearview mirror.</p> <p></p> <p><b><i>The Playboy</i></b></p> <p>He’s the town’s most popular playboy.</p> <p>She’s sworn off men and weddings for good.</p> <p></p> <p><b><i>The Heartbreaker</i></b></p> <p>He’s a loner who indulges in a one-night stand out of town.</p> <p>She’s a senator’s daughter who never expects to see her indulgence again.</p>"; 
